<p id="notice"><%= notice %></p>




<h4>Imagine what could happen if everyone in the planet is telling us how many junk mail they get everyday. </h4>
<h4>How many unnecessary mail circulates every day? We really want to know and need your help!</h4>

<h1> Top Companies Sending Junk Mail </h1>
<%= chart_stacked_company_name %>

<% if user_signed_in? %>
  <%= link_to 'New Mail', new_mail_path, class: "btn btn-default" %>
<% else %>
  <h4>Please Sign in and let us know how many Junk mail you got today.</h4>
  <img src="http://www1.nyc.gov/assets/greenyc/images/content/titles/junk_mail_header.jpg" width="300" >
<% end %>



<table class="table table-hover">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Company</th>
      <th>Quantity</th>
      <th colspan="3"></th>
    </tr>
  </thead>

  <tbody>
    <% @companies.each do |company| %>
      <tr>
        <td><%= company.name %></td>
        <td><%= company.company_size %></td>
      </tr>
    <% end %>
  </tbody>
</table>

